org.embulk.spi

Interface GuessPlugin


  • public interface GuessPlugin
    The main class that a Guess Plugin implements.

    A Guess Plugin guesses a configuration ConfigDiff from a partial configuration for input, and a byte sequence Buffer.

    Since:
    0.4.0
